            "content": "Small summary of each tool with the features and results that I got. This section not follows any special order."
        },
        {
            "heading": "Bheem",
            "subheadings": [
                {
                    "heading": "Pros",
                    "type": "list",
                    "content": [
                        "Superb workflow.",
                        "Easy to understand and adapt for your needs.",
                        "Best and trendy tools like nuclei, dalfox or gf patterns.",
                        "Scope defined workflows."
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "heading": "Cons",
                    "type": "list",
                    "content": [
                        "No web screenshots.",
                        "Lack of output customization."
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "heading": "3klcon",
            "subheadings": [
